    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices:
        - Report Info: Plan's 3-phase progression (Foundation, Strength, Power). Goal: Show change/progress over time. Viz: A horizontal bar chart (Chart.js) visually quantifies the shifting focus of each phase from mobility to strength and power. Interaction: None, it's a summary graphic. Justification: Provides an immediate, at-a-glance understanding of the plan's arc, which is more motivating than text alone.
        - Report Info: Core principles. Goal: Inform/Reinforce. Presentation: A prominent, easily readable list at the top. Justification: These are the ground rules for recovery and must be front and center.
        - Report Info: Daily exercise lists. Goal: Organize/Inform. Presentation: Tabbed content sections for Weeks, with nested accordions/sections for Days. Exercises are displayed in distinct 'cards'. Justification: This hierarchical structure allows the user to drill down from the high-level phase to the specific daily workout without being overwhelmed by the entire 6-week plan at once.
    -->
