                <p class="text-center text-slate-600 mb-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">This plan is divided into three distinct phases, each lasting two weeks. The focus will gradually shift from building a stable foundation to developing running-specific power, ensuring you're ready and resilient when you return to the road.</p>
