                                    <p class="text-sm text-amber-600 font-semibold mb-2">3 sets of 10-12 reps per side</p>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Lie on back, arms to ceiling, knees at 90°. Extend opposite arm and leg, keeping lower back on floor.</p>
