                                    <p class="text-sm text-amber-600 font-semibold mb-2">Hold 30-60 seconds per side</p>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Focus on the uninjured hip. Gently lean forward. Avoid any pressure on the injured foot.</p>
