                        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg">
                             <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-xl">Active Recovery & Mobility</h4>
                             <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Focus on longer holds, deeper stretches, and mindful movement. Repeat exercises from Sunday or Monday, but use slower, more controlled movements. For example, try 60-second planks or 90-second stretches.</p>
